    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The powertrain remains robust, with the critical VANOS system serviced and the rod bearing maintenance addressed to preserve the 8,000 RPM redline integrity. The chassis has been enhanced with subframe reinforcement, ensuring the structural rigidity necessary for the variable M-differential to deliver optimal torque bias. While showing minor cosmetic patina, the mechanicals are sound, featuring a firm suspension geometry and responsive individual throttle bodies that provide immediate throttle mapping. A mechanically sound specimen for the enthusiast who prioritizes drivetrain performance and analog feedback.",
